description: The A Cloud Guru app will help you prepare for the Certified Solutions Architect Associate exam by asking you practice exam questions. The app has over 200 practice exam questions and each game consists of 10 random question. Build out your AWS exam knowledge today.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask A Cloud Guru to start a new exam
Alexa, ask A Cloud Guru to start a new quiz
name: A Cloud Guru
shortDescription: Are you studying for your Amazon Web Services Solutions Architect Associate exam? This Alexa app will help you study by asking you practice exam questions.
